\hline COLOUR & USE & ADDITIVES \\
\hline Gray & Plasma, whole blood (glycolysis inhibitor) & Fluoride( $\mathrm{Na}+$ ), oxalate ( $\mathrm{Na}+, \mathrm{K}+$ ) or iodoacetate (NA+) \\
\hline Yellow & Sterile & None \\
\hline Green & Plasma ,whole blood & Heparin ( $\mathrm{Na}+$, Li or NH4) \\
\hline Red & serum & None \\
\hline Blue & Plasma or whole blood & Citrate ( $\mathrm{Na}+$ ) \\
\hline Lavender & Plasma or whole blood & EDTA \\
